  "commit_message": "fix(activations): remove invocation_type from Attachment and state.json\n\nThe `invocation_type` field on `Attachment` was added to support a\nconsumer that never shipped (DEV-82); it has no current reader, so\npersisting it on every activation is dead weight in `state.json` and a\nmaintenance liability in the activation API. This removes the field\nentirely — from the `Attachment` struct, the `start_or_attach`/`start`\nsignatures, and every call site across the activate, attach, detach,\nand executive ",
